divs: sighting detailson 12\8\10 i was driving home from dublin on 33 west at approximately 4:25pm. it was a sunny and clear day. in the sw sky i spotted a shiny metallic cylinder-shaped object with a second one below it slightly moving back and forth as if suspended from the one above it. both cylinders were vertical and slowly falling straight downward. between trying to keep my eye on them and the road, i lost sight of it. it certainly was not a plane and i saw it well before the marysville airport, i'd say about 7 miles. there was one thing about the bottom cylinder that just looked different and it come to mind a day or two later that is wasn't quite shaped like the top one. i believe the one beneath was damaged just by the shape of it. after seeing the objects i became very excited and couldn't wait to get home and write down what i'd witnessed and was certain, with all the traffic around me, that someone else had to have witnessed it too. i can still see the objects in my mind as if i am witnessing them over and over again.
Summary: Sighted Two Cylinders in Marysville Area
